node.text:
The lake was not cold enough anymore!😅so I found this place!🥶🧊 

Some more impressions of my recovery in the next slides!🏋️‍♂️💪💯

1️⃣ the worst is always to go in!🥶💦 
2️⃣ brain freeze to finish it off!🧠❄️ 
3️⃣ Improving everyday in Physio-Therapy!💯
4️⃣ Water-Therapy right after!🚶‍♂️ 🏊‍♂️ 
5️⃣ Back on skis! ⛷ LoL 
6️⃣ working on the remaining muscles!💪
7️⃣ Air squat!😅🏋️‍♂️ 
8️⃣ slowly learning how to walk again!🚶‍♂️ 
9️⃣ reading a book while icing the knee!💆‍♂️ 📚 
🔟 instagram vs. reality!🤣

#IceBath #Recovery #Spring #Sunny #Flims #AtHome #Wimhof #Challenge #Cold #ColdBath #ColdExposure #WimHofMethod #ColdTherapy #Nature #Panasonic #S1H
